  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A prospective, non-randomized multi-center clinical evaluation of the performance of the
      TriVascular Thoracic Stent Graft System when used in the treatment of subjects with thoracic
      aortic aneurysms (TAA).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
